value.0:
This note appears to have been torn from another peice of parchment. There is a portion you cannot read, right at the top, but the bottom says,
"Don't worry about the local girl, I can take care of her. This new meat is beginning to grate. Remove it and you will have my gratitude and, as always, your regular fee."
